---
import Layout from "@/layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="About - usestore">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4 py-12 md:py-16">
    <!-- Hero -->
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center mb-8">
      <h1 class="text-2xl font-medium">About usestore</h1>
      <p class="text-muted-foreground mt-2">
        We believe in quality essentials that stand the test of time. Our mission is to create timeless pieces that become the foundation of your wardrobe.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Story -->
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 md:gap-12 items-center mb-12">
      <div class="aspect-[4/3] bg-muted flex items-center justify-center text-muted-foreground/30">
        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="48" height="48" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
          <rect width="18" height="18" x="3" y="3" rx="2" ry="2"></rect>
          <circle cx="9" cy="9" r="2"></circle>
          <path d="m21 15-3.086-3.086a2 2 0 0 0-2.828 0L6 21"></path>
        </svg>
      </div>
      <div>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-medium mb-6">Our Story</h2>
        <div class="space-y-4 text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed">
          <p>
            Founded in 2020, usestore was born from a simple idea: create clothing that you'll want to wear every day, year after year. We noticed the fashion industry was full of disposable trends, and we wanted to offer an alternative.
          </p>
          <p>
            Our approach is simple. We focus on perfect fits, premium materials, and classic designs that never go out of style. Every piece in our collection is designed to be versatile, comfortable, and built to last.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Values -->
    <div class="mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-lg font-medium text-center mb-6">Our Values</h2>
      <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-8">
        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 mx-auto mb-4 bg-muted flex items-center justify-center text-muted-foreground">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
              <path d="M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10"></path>
              <path d="m9 12 2 2 4-4"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-medium mb-2">Quality First</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-muted-foreground">
            We never compromise on materials or craftsmanship. Every stitch matters.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 mx-auto mb-4 bg-muted flex items-center justify-center text-muted-foreground">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
              <path d="M12 3a6 6 0 0 0 9 9 9 9 0 1 1-9-9Z"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-medium mb-2">Sustainable</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-muted-foreground">
            We're committed to reducing our environmental impact through responsible practices.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 mx-auto mb-4 bg-muted flex items-center justify-center text-muted-foreground">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
              <path d="M16 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H6a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2"></path>
              <circle cx="9" cy="7" r="4"></circle>
              <path d="M22 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-3-3.87"></path>
              <path d="M16 3.13a4 4 0 0 1 0 7.75"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-medium mb-2">Community</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-muted-foreground">
            We treat our customers, partners, and team members like family.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 mx-auto mb-4 bg-muted flex items-center justify-center text-muted-foreground">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
              <path d="M6 9H4.5a2.5 2.5 0 0 1 0-5H6"></path>
              <path d="M18 9h1.5a2.5 2.5 0 0 0 0-5H18"></path>
              <path d="M4 22h16"></path>
              <path d="M10 14.66V17c0 .55-.47.98-.97 1.21C7.85 18.75 7 20.24 7 22"></path>
              <path d="M14 14.66V17c0 .55.47.98.97 1.21C16.15 18.75 17 20.24 17 22"></path>
              <path d="M18 2H6v7a6 6 0 0 0 12 0V2Z"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-medium mb-2">Timeless Design</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-muted-foreground">
            We create pieces that transcend seasons and trends.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Team -->
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 md:gap-12 items-center">
      <div class="order-2 md:order-1">
        <h2 class="text-lg font-medium mb-6">Our Team</h2>
        <div class="space-y-4 text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed">
          <p>
            We're a small, dedicated team of designers, craftspeople, and customer advocates. Based in San Francisco, we work closely with manufacturers who share our commitment to quality and ethical production.
          </p>
          <p>
            Every member of our team is passionate about creating clothes that people genuinely love to wear. We're always looking for talented individuals to join us.
          </p>
        </div>
        <a href="/careers" class="inline-block mt-6 py-2.5 px-6 border border-input text-sm font-medium hover:bg-muted">
          View Open Positions
        </a>
      </div>
      <div class="aspect-[4/3] bg-muted flex items-center justify-center text-muted-foreground/30 order-1 md:order-2">
        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="48" height="48" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
          <rect width="18" height="18" x="3" y="3" rx="2" ry="2"></rect>
          <circle cx="9" cy="9" r="2"></circle>
          <path d="m21 15-3.086-3.086a2 2 0 0 0-2.828 0L6 21"></path>
        </svg>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
